00:00:02.120 --> 00:00:03.054
HEY EVERYONE...

00:00:03.054 --> 00:00:04.834
WELCOME BACK TO MOVIE RECAP.

00:00:04.834 --> 00:00:06.940
TODAY I'M GONNA SHOW YOU A MOVIE CALLED

00:00:06.940 --> 00:00:08.100
COUNTDOWN...

00:00:08.100 --> 00:00:11.255
IT IS A 2019 AMERICAN SUPERNATURAL HORROR FILM

00:00:11.255 --> 00:00:13.131
DIRECTED AND WRITTEN BY JUSTIN DEC,

00:00:13.131 --> 00:00:14.867
AND STARRING ELIZABETH LAIL.

00:00:14.867 --> 00:00:17.466
THE MOVIE IS ABOUT A NURSE WHO DOWNLOADS AN APP

00:00:17.466 --> 00:00:20.176
THAT CLAIMS TO PREDICT THE MOMENT A PERSON WILL DIE,

00:00:20.176 --> 00:00:22.516
IT TELLS HER SHE ONLY HAS THREE DAYS TO LIVE.

00:00:22.516 --> 00:00:24.214
LET’S START...

00:00:33.376 --> 00:00:34.236
AT A PARTY,

00:00:34.236 --> 00:00:36.308
TEENAGER COURTNEY IS CONVINCED BY HER FRIENDS

00:00:36.308 --> 00:00:37.632
TO DOWNLOAD COUNTDOWN,

00:00:37.632 --> 00:00:39.587
AN APP THAT SEEMINGLY PREDICTS

00:00:39.587 --> 00:00:41.522
HOW LONG A USER HAS LEFT TO LIVE.

00:00:41.522 --> 00:00:45.242
COURTNEY IS STARTLED THAT IT SAYS SHE HAS ONLY 3 HOURS TO LIVES.

00:00:45.242 --> 00:00:48.800
AFTER AVOIDING GETTING INTO A CAR WITH HER DRUNK BOYFRIEND EVAN,

00:00:48.800 --> 00:00:51.114
COURTNEY RECEIVES A NOTIFICATION STATING

00:00:51.114 --> 00:00:53.033
THAT SHE HAS BROKEN THE "USER AGREEMENT".

00:00:53.033 --> 00:00:54.135
RETURNING HOME,

00:00:54.135 --> 00:00:56.190
SHE IS ATTACKED BY AN UNSEEN ENTITY

00:00:56.190 --> 00:00:58.503
AND KILLED AS HER TIMER REACHES ZERO.

00:00:58.503 --> 00:00:59.612
AT THE SAME TIME,

00:00:59.612 --> 00:01:01.393
EVAN CRASHES AND A TREE BRANCH

00:01:01.393 --> 00:01:04.011
GOES RIGHT THROUGH WHERE COURTNEY WOULD HAVE SAT.

00:01:04.830 --> 00:01:05.913
ON THE NEXT SCENE,

00:01:05.913 --> 00:01:08.615
QUINN HARRIS IS A NURSE THAT WORKS AT THE HOSPITAL

00:01:08.615 --> 00:01:10.064
WHERE AN INJURED EVAN IS ADMITTED.

00:01:10.064 --> 00:01:13.325
SHE SUFFERS FREQUENT SEXUAL HARASSMENT BY HER BOSS,

00:01:13.325 --> 00:01:14.240
DOCTOR SULLIVAN,

00:01:14.240 --> 00:01:16.310
BUT FEARS SPEAKING OUT AS SHE HAS ONLY

00:01:16.310 --> 00:01:18.427
JUST PASSED HER EXAM TO BE AN RA.

00:01:18.427 --> 00:01:21.784
QUINN STUMBLES ACROSS EVAN IN A CLOSED-OFF WING OF THE HOSPITAL

00:01:21.784 --> 00:01:25.042
WHERE HE TELLS HER ABOUT COURTNEY AND HIS SUSPICIONS ABOUT THE APP.

00:01:25.042 --> 00:01:27.359
HE ALSO REVEALS THAT HE DOWNLOADED IT

00:01:27.359 --> 00:01:30.899
AND IT STATES THAT HE WILL DIE AT THE TIME HE IS DUE TO GO INTO SURGERY.

00:01:30.899 --> 00:01:32.769
QUINN IS DISMISSIVE OF HIS CLAIMS

00:01:32.769 --> 00:01:34.604
BUT EVENTUALLY DOWNLOADS THE APP

00:01:34.604 --> 00:01:36.410
AFTER HER CO-WORKERS DOWNLOAD IT.

00:01:36.410 --> 00:01:38.891
SHE IS HORRIFIED TO LEARN THAT IT SAYS SHE HAS

00:01:38.891 --> 00:01:40.250
ONLY THREE DAYS LEFT.

00:01:40.250 --> 00:01:43.012
EVAN LATER SKIPS HIS SURGERY AND IS INFORMED

00:01:43.012 --> 00:01:45.639
THAT HE HAS VIOLATED THE USER AGREEMENT OF THE APP.

00:01:45.639 --> 00:01:47.974
HE IS CONFRONTED BY A DEMONIC VERSION OF

00:01:47.974 --> 00:01:49.397
COURTNEY AND KILLED.

00:01:49.397 --> 00:01:52.519
QUINN VISITS HER HOME TO PICK UP AN IMPORTANT DOCUMENT

00:01:52.519 --> 00:01:54.733
AND ENCOUNTERS HER YOUNGER SISTER JORDAN

00:01:54.733 --> 00:01:56.335
WHO HAS A STRAINED RELATIONSHIP WITH HER

00:01:56.335 --> 00:01:58.102
FOLLOWING THEIR MOTHER'S DEATH.

00:01:58.102 --> 00:02:00.391
THE NEXT DAY, QUINN LEARNS OF EVAN'S DEATH

00:02:00.391 --> 00:02:01.917
AND PROCURES HIS PHONE.

00:02:01.917 --> 00:02:03.362
SHE CANCELS A PLAN

00:02:03.362 --> 00:02:05.301
TO GO OUT WITH JORDAN AND THEIR FATHER

00:02:05.301 --> 00:02:06.504
BEFORE BEING INFORMED

00:02:06.504 --> 00:02:08.759
THAT SHE HAS BROKEN THE USER AGREEMENT.

00:02:09.790 --> 00:02:11.994
SHE IS THEN HARASSED YET AGAIN BY SULLIVAN

00:02:11.994 --> 00:02:13.199
BEFORE FLEEING.

00:02:13.199 --> 00:02:14.731
QUINN RESEARCHES ABOUT THE APP,

00:02:14.731 --> 00:02:17.351
LEARNING OF COURTNEY'S DEATH AND THAT SIMILAR THINGS

00:02:17.351 --> 00:02:18.923
HAVE HAPPENED TO OTHER APP USERS

00:02:18.923 --> 00:02:21.204
ALTHOUGH THEY ARE WIDELY REGARDED AS FAKE.

00:02:21.204 --> 00:02:22.836
SHE IS STARTLED BY A VISION OF A

00:02:22.836 --> 00:02:25.480
DEAD EVAN AND FLEES HER APARTMENT.

00:02:28.299 --> 00:02:30.103
SHE IS FOUND THE NEXT DAY BY JORDAN

00:02:30.103 --> 00:02:31.815
AND JORDAN LEARNS ABOUT THE APP WHICH

00:02:31.815 --> 00:02:33.979
STATES QUINN ONLY HAS ONE DAY LEFT.

00:02:33.979 --> 00:02:35.330
INCREASINGLY PANICKED,

00:02:35.330 --> 00:02:36.998
QUINN BUYS A NEW PHONE

00:02:36.998 --> 00:02:39.278
BUT DISCOVERS THE COUNTDOWN APP HAS INSTALLED

00:02:39.278 --> 00:02:40.981
ITSELF ON THE NEW PHONE.

00:02:42.550 --> 00:02:44.808
AFTER BEING ATTACKED BY A DEMONIC FIGURE,

00:02:44.808 --> 00:02:46.141
SHE ENCOUNTERS MATT,

00:02:46.141 --> 00:02:47.671
WHOSE COUNTDOWN APP STATES

00:02:47.671 --> 00:02:50.182
HE WILL DIE A FEW HOURS BEFORE QUINN.

00:02:52.349 --> 00:02:53.644
THE PAIR HEAD TO THE HOSPITAL

00:02:53.644 --> 00:02:55.581
TO GET HELP FROM THE HOSPITAL'S PRIEST,

00:02:55.581 --> 00:02:57.405
ONLY FOR QUINN TO LEARN THAT SULLIVAN

00:02:57.405 --> 00:02:59.075
HAS TRICKED THE STAFF INTO THINKING

00:02:59.075 --> 00:03:00.540
THAT SHE SEXUALLY HARASSED HIM

00:03:00.540 --> 00:03:02.805
AND AS A RESULT, QUINN IS SUSPENDED.

00:03:02.805 --> 00:03:04.310
MATT IS ATTACKED BY THE ENTITY

00:03:04.310 --> 00:03:05.927
TAKING THE FORM OF HIS YOUNGER BROTHER

00:03:05.927 --> 00:03:07.679
WHO DIED OF AN ILLNESS YEARS AGO.

00:03:09.117 --> 00:03:10.471
THE PAIR LEAVE THE HOSPITAL

00:03:10.471 --> 00:03:12.021
AND BEGIN TO SUSPECT THAT SOMETHING

00:03:12.021 --> 00:03:14.028
IN THE USER AGREEMENT MAY HELP THEM.

00:03:14.028 --> 00:03:15.963
IT STATES THE AGREEMENT IS BROKEN

00:03:15.963 --> 00:03:18.077
IF THE USER TRIES TO CHANGE THEIR FATE

00:03:18.077 --> 00:03:20.617
AND THEY REALIZE THAT THEY HAVE CANCELED PLANS.

00:03:20.617 --> 00:03:22.815
THEY CONSULT A PRIEST CALLED FATHER JOHN

00:03:22.815 --> 00:03:25.324
WHO STATES THAT THE APP'S CODE MAY HELP THEM.

00:03:25.324 --> 00:03:28.137
THEY HACK INTO THE CODE WITH THE HELP OF A PHONE SALESMAN

00:03:28.137 --> 00:03:31.008
NAMED DEREK AND LEARN THAT JORDAN HAS DOWNLOADED THE APP

00:03:31.008 --> 00:03:33.388
AND DUE TO DIE SHORTLY BEFORE QUINN.

00:03:33.388 --> 00:03:35.049
THEY HACK THE APP TO ADD MORE YEARS

00:03:35.049 --> 00:03:36.348
TO THEIR LIFE SPAN

00:03:36.348 --> 00:03:38.087
BUT QUINN IS ATTACKED BY THE DEMON

00:03:38.087 --> 00:03:38.848
LATER THAT NIGHT

00:03:38.848 --> 00:03:41.669
AND THE COUNTDOWNS REVERT BACK TO NORMAL.

00:03:42.480 --> 00:03:44.532
AFTER JORDAN IS ATTACKED BY THE DEMON

00:03:44.532 --> 00:03:45.953
WHO TAKES THE FORM OF HER MOTHER,

00:03:45.953 --> 00:03:47.869
THE TRIO CONSULTS FATHER JOHN

00:03:47.869 --> 00:03:50.133
WHO IDENTIFIES THE DEMON NAME OZHIN,

00:03:50.133 --> 00:03:52.463
AND CURSE VIA THE APP CODE BEFORE THEORIZING

00:03:52.463 --> 00:03:55.172
IF THEY BEAT THE COUNTDOWN TIMER BY ONE SECOND

00:03:55.172 --> 00:03:56.228
THEN THEY'LL WIN.

00:03:56.228 --> 00:03:57.842
THEY PREPARE A WARDING CIRCLE TO

00:03:57.842 --> 00:03:59.737
PROTECT THEM FROM THE OZHIN'S ATTACKS

00:03:59.737 --> 00:04:01.467
BUT MATT IS LURED OUT BY THE OZHIN

00:04:01.467 --> 00:04:03.242
TAKING THE FORM OF HIS BROTHER.

00:04:03.242 --> 00:04:05.548
MATT ENDS UP GETTING HIT BY A CAR AND KILLED

00:04:05.548 --> 00:04:08.822
 AS HIS LAST BREATH EXPIRES WHEN THE APP SAID.

00:04:11.756 --> 00:04:13.920
JORDAN IS ALSO INJURED IN THE ATTACK

00:04:13.920 --> 00:04:15.549
AND QUINN TAKES HER TO THE HOSPITAL

00:04:15.549 --> 00:04:17.612
WHERE SHE LEARNS THAT SULLIVAN ALSO HARASSES

00:04:17.612 --> 00:04:19.613
OTHER FEMALE STAFF MEMBERS.

00:04:19.613 --> 00:04:21.335
REALIZING THAT SHE COULD KILL SULLIVAN

00:04:21.335 --> 00:04:23.114
AND TAKE THE 57 YEARS HIS

00:04:23.114 --> 00:04:24.951
COUNTDOWN APP PREDICTED FOR HIM,

00:04:24.951 --> 00:04:26.731
QUINN LURES HIM INTO THE CLOSED-OFF WING

00:04:26.731 --> 00:04:29.073
AND ATTACKS HIM BUT HE IS SAVED BY THE OZHIN 

00:04:29.073 --> 00:04:31.026
WHO REALIZES WHAT SHE IS DOING.

00:04:33.132 --> 00:04:34.606
THE OZHIN HUNTS DOWN JORDAN

00:04:34.606 --> 00:04:36.308
AS QUINN SEARCHES FOR SULLIVAN

00:04:36.308 --> 00:04:38.290
WHO ESCAPES AFTER QUINN IS INJURED.

00:04:39.576 --> 00:04:41.428
THE OZHIN PREPARES TO KILL JORDAN

00:04:41.428 --> 00:04:42.890
AS HER TIMER RUNS OUT

00:04:42.890 --> 00:04:44.748
BUT QUINN OVERDOSES ON DRUGS,

00:04:44.748 --> 00:04:47.433
SACRIFICING HERSELF TO DESTROYING THE OZHIN.

00:04:47.433 --> 00:04:49.369
JORDAN NOTICES THAT QUINN HAS WRITTEN

00:04:49.369 --> 00:04:50.425
SOMETHING ON HER ARM

00:04:50.425 --> 00:04:51.852
WHERE SHE DREW HERSELF A CIRCLE

00:04:51.852 --> 00:04:53.280
AND THE WORD "NARCAN".

00:04:53.280 --> 00:04:55.823
JORDAN REVIVES HER BY SYRINGE WITH NALOXONE

00:04:55.823 --> 00:04:57.239
AND THE DUO SUCCEED AS THE

00:04:57.239 --> 00:04:59.684
COUNTDOWN TIMERS FOR THEM BOTH STOP.

00:05:00.800 --> 00:05:03.628
LATER, QUINN, JORDAN AND THEIR FATHER

00:05:03.628 --> 00:05:05.156
VISIT THEIR MOTHER'S GRAVE.

00:05:05.156 --> 00:05:06.248
AS THEY LEAVE,

00:05:06.248 --> 00:05:08.155
THEY HEAR NEWS ABOUT SULLIVAN'S ARREST

00:05:08.155 --> 00:05:09.959
AFTER MORE NURSES CAME FORWARD

00:05:09.959 --> 00:05:12.838
AND TOLD THEIR SIMILAR STORIES OF SEXUAL ASSAULT.

00:05:12.838 --> 00:05:14.971
QUINN DISCOVERS AN UPDATE OF THE NEW APP

00:05:14.971 --> 00:05:16.899
COUNTDOWN 2.0 HAS DOWNLOADED

00:05:16.899 --> 00:05:18.209
ITSELF ON HER PHONE.

00:05:19.310 --> 00:05:20.559
IN A MID-CREDIT SCENE,

00:05:20.559 --> 00:05:22.270
A PHONE SALESMAN, DEREK

00:05:22.270 --> 00:05:23.702
IS ON A 'TINDER' DATE.

00:05:23.702 --> 00:05:25.537
WHILE HIS DATE GOES TO THE BATHROOM,

00:05:25.537 --> 00:05:26.921
DEREK'S PHONE BUZZES,

00:05:26.921 --> 00:05:27.640
HE LOOKS AT IT

00:05:27.640 --> 00:05:28.907
